org.ggp.base.util.gdl

Class GdlVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ggp.base.util.gdl.GdlVisitor

  • public abstract class GdlVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
    A visitor for Gdl objects. The GdlVisitors class has methods for going through a Gdl object or collection thereof and applying the visitor methods to all relevant Gdl objects. This visitor uses the adapter design pattern, providing empty implementations of each method so subclasses need only implement the relevant methods.
    Author:
    Alex Landau
